caption: A girl in a green dress has collected a lot of wood from the forest.
Three boys are standing together in local clothes and hats
A woman with a blue scarf is sitting by a pool of water.
A girl in an orange dress is sitting on the carpets spread on the roof
The baker man in white clothes is holding a loaf of bread.
Two girls with red and green shawls standing on the paintings on the street floor

Two women in tents, one of them holding several books, come down the stairs.

Three men are sitting on a chair and one of them is talking.
